Package com.arkoisystems.arkoicompiler.stage.syntaxAnalyzer.ast.utils

  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ASTAccess
    This enum defines the different access levels for various ASTs like FunctionInvokeOperableSyntaxAST, IdentifierInvokeOperableSyntaxAST etc.
    ASTType
    This enum contains for every AST one entry to differentiate these from each other.
    BlockType
    This enum is used to define the BlockType for an BlockSyntaxAST.
    TypeKind
    This enum is used to define a TypeKind which is used in TypeSyntaxAST.
